# Phase 2 — THE FINAL SWITCH. These protected case-data files are served from a
# PRIVATE Cloudflare R2 bucket via /api/asset (subscription-gated), so they must NOT
# ship to the public Vercel CDN.
#
# WARNING: once this file is on `main`, the listed assets disappear from the CDN and the
# trainer loads them ONLY through /api/asset. Do not merge to production until R2 is
# populated (scripts/upload-to-r2.mjs) AND the R2_*/CLERK_* env vars are set in Vercel
# for the Production environment — otherwise the live trainer breaks for everyone.

